-- Marubeni to Spend $700 Million on LNG Venture With BW Gas, Nikkei Reports
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2010-10-13T20:17:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/marubeni-to-spend-700-million-on-lng-venture-with-bw-gas-nikkei-reports.html
Marubeni Corp. plans to spend $700
million in a venture with BW Gas AS that will take control of
eight BW Gas tankers for shipping liquefied natural gas, Nikkei
English News said, without citing anyone.  Marubeni will hold 49 percent of the venture, with BW Gas
having 51 percent, according to the report.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  